{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDQ2NTAzNTgz", "number": 7305, "title": "Assign overflow source tabs to correct columns", "bodyText": "Selecting the overflow chevron previously only displayed the tabs of the active column, now the tabs for that specific column are displayed and selecting a column to switch to works as expected.\nPreviously, the drop down menu learned the state of the source tabs from an event triggered by a source column. Now that we have multiple source columns, the menu needs more knowledge about where the change is coming from. I've removed DocTabsChangedEvent so that the column communicates directly to its menu. The Source Column's chevron button's click handler needed to be updated to notify the SourceColumnManager to set the active column on selection.", "createdAt": "2020-07-08T21:50:43Z", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/7305", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "209c94a941f51ec7c1e057a288102c89a47f3de8"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-07-09T22:43:14Z", "author": {"login": "melissa-barca"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 5, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABczBTmaAH2gAyNDQ2NTAzNTgzOjViY2EzYTAwZGQ5NGVjOGYwMWYzOTMxZTdmMTBiNDQwZjM2NzA4MjI=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABczW9SAAFqTQ0NjAxNTc0NQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "5bca3a00dd94ec8f01f3931e7f10b440f3670822", "author": {"user": {"login": "melissa-barca", "name": "Melissa Barca"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/5bca3a00dd94ec8f01f3931e7f10b440f3670822", "committedDate": "2020-07-08T21:27:32Z", "message": "remove DocTabsChangedEvent and update docs status directly through the view"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "e0c36e166921fe833ea149bffc8b2139aaaf3a31", "author": {"user": {"login": "melissa-barca", "name": "Melissa Barca"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/e0c36